# Autodarts Tools Tech Stack

This document defines the technology stack used in the Autodarts Tools project.

## Languages
- TypeScript
- Vue

## Frameworks
- Vue 3.x
- WXT (Web Extension Toolkit) - For building browser extensions
- TailwindCSS 3.x

## Libraries
- VueUse - Collection of Vue Composition Utilities
- Radix Vue - UI component library
- Iconify - Icons in CSS mode (from https://iconify.design/docs/usage/css/)
- tailwind-merge - For handling dynamic class merging in Vue components

## Custom Components
Button: AppButton.vue
Input: AppInput.vue
Textarea: AppTextarea.vue
Notification: AppNotification.vue
Radio Group: AppRadioGroup.vue
Select: AppSelect
Tabs: AppTabs
Confirm Dialog: ConfirmDialog.vue
Modal: AppModal.vue

## Build Tools
- Vite - Build tool and dev server
- TypeScript 5.x

## Project Configuration
- Package Manager: Yarn
- Project Type: Browser Extension

## Development Conventions
- Component Format: Vue Single File Components (.vue)
- State Management: Vue Composition API
- CSS Framework: TailwindCSS